OL,3,CTeen waiting to go to college because
OL,4,Cof paperwork delay
OL,6,FA teenager from Lancashire has been
OL,7,Ftold he must wait even longer to start
OL,8,Fcollege because of council delays in
OL,9,Fgetting him the right paperwork.
OL,11,FTomas Woods should be in college right
OL,12,Fnow, but because of council paperwork
OL,13,Fhold ups he's still stuck at home.
OL,15,FHe was told he needed an EHCP from the
OL,16,FCounty Council, a special educational
OL,17,Fhealth and care plan to pay for his
OL,18,Fextra requirements.
