OL,3,CTeen waiting to go to college because
OL,4,Cof paperwork delay
OL,6,FBut exactly a month since he raised
OL,7,Fhis concerns with Granada Reports he's
OL,8,Fstill waiting.
OL,10,FHe said: "Its really disappointing cos
OL,11,Fby now we're another month on - it
OL,12,Fshould've just been done by this point
OL,13,Fand there's really no excuse for it
OL,14,Fnot to have been."
OL,16,FThe EHCP is a legal document that
OL,17,Foutlines the needs of a young person
OL,18,Fwith a disability and the support they
OL,19,Frequire
