OL,3,CTeen waiting to go to college because
OL,4,Cof paperwork delay
OL,6,FIt should have been finalised by
OL,7,FLancashire County Council by the end
OL,8,Fof March - but in October he's still
OL,9,Fwaiting for the document that would
OL,10,Fenable him to begin at a specialist
OL,11,Fcollege - and he's just one of more
OL,12,Fthan a thousand complaints the council
OL,13,Fhas received about its SEND services.
OL,15,FAnd it doesn't end there for Tomas -
OL,16,Fhe is also the current wheelchair
OL,17,Fmotocross world champion but that is
OL,18,Falso being out at risk without the EHCP
