OL,6,FTomas's story is by no means unique
OL,7,Fand a special helpline set up at the
OL,8,Fstart of September has been
OL,9,Foverwhelmed.
OL,11,FIn a statement Lancashire County
OL,12,FCouncil say, "Now that Tomas is 16,
OL,13,Fthe council has taken over arranging
OL,14,Fthe provision contained in his
OL,15,FEducation, Health and Care Plan( EHCP)
OL,16,Fand need to ensure that this still
OL,17,Fcovers him for all of his activities.
