OL,6,F"Tomas is an exceptional young athlete
OL,7,Fand his situation is unique. We need
OL,8,Fto ensure that his EHCP and insurance
OL,9,Fpolicies are up to date and we are
OL,10,Fsorry that this has taken longer than
OL,11,Fanticipated.
OL,13,F"We are working towards a solution as
OL,14,Fa matter of the utmost priority.
OL,15,FCreativity Works provide Tomas with
OL,16,Fhis educational provision, and we are
OL,17,Fin the process of making plans for him
OL,18,Fto return to this in the very near
OL,19,Ffuture."
